 that would suffice in being dramatic or coy, but I may say this: A man must not forget what it was to be a boy..." <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=687935" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=687935</a></td></td></tr>
